<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #f8fbff;
      --muted: #bdd0e8;
      --blue: #4aa6ff;
      --orange: #f08a2a;
      --bg: #081525;
    }
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      align-items: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 26%, rgba(74, 166, 255, 0.28), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(140deg, #081525 0%, #102647 60%, #07101e 100%);
      color: var(--ink);
      display: flex;
      font-family: "Hiragino Sans", "Yu Gothic", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
      height: 1080px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      width: 1920px;
    }
    .rings {
      border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      border-radius: 50%;
      height: 900px;
      position: absolute;
      width: 900px;
    }
    .rings::before,
    .rings::after {
      border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
      border-radius: 50%;
      content: "";
      inset: 110px;
      position: absolute;
    }
    .rings::after {
      inset: 230px;
    }
    .panel {
      align-items: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
      text-align: center;
      width: 1280px;
    }
    .label {
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 86px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing: -0.045em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .message {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-top: 38px;
    }
    .bar {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--orange));
      border-radius: 999px;
      height: 12px;
      margin-top: 56px;
      width: 480px;
    }
    .footer {
      bottom: 44px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      position: absolute;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="rings"></div>
  <main class="panel">
    <div class="label">OWLCLAW NEWS</div>
    <h1>本日のAIニュースは<br>以上です</h1>
    <div class="message">詳細はオブシディアンのデイリーダイジェストで確認できます。</div>
    <div class="bar"></div>
  </main>
  <div class="footer">{{ deck.date }}</div>
</body>
</html>
